Definition: of insufficient quantity to meet a need
Example: an inadequate income; a poor salary; money is short; on short rations; food is in short supply; short on experience; the jejune diets of the very poor
Synonyms: noun, attribute, inadequateness, poor, poorness, short, state, shortness, jejune, jejuneness, jejunity, of, insufficient, quantity, to, meet, a, need, an, income, salary, money, is, on, rations, food, in, supply, experience, the, diets, very
Category: adj.all
